Packages 
Package Description
bluej.codecoverage  
bluej.codecoverage.main
Contains classes for setting up the extension when BlueJ initializes it.
bluej.codecoverage.pref
Classes for accessing preferences defined in the option package.
bluej.codecoverage.pref.option
Contains classes that provide access to specific preferences.
bluej.codecoverage.ui.button
Classes for rendering and adding functionality to the button that starts and stops code coverage.
bluej.codecoverage.ui.ext
Classes that define additional behavior to add to the source code display.
bluej.codecoverage.ui.main
Classes for displaying the main report frame that appears after a Coverage session.
bluej.codecoverage.ui.pref
Class for the preference panel displayed by BlueJ.
bluej.codecoverage.utils
Contains general utility classes, and classes for starting coverage sessions, and gathering the results.
bluej.codecoverage.utils.join
Classes that combines the coverage information in bluej.codecoverage.utils.serial, with the BlueJ objects that the coverage information is for.
bluej.codecoverage.utils.serial
Beans for Jacoco's coverage information.
